# ROADMAP — {{project_name}}

A milestone-based plan, not a calendar. Each milestone is a coherent slice of value that can be released and used. We finish each one before starting the next.

> **Dates are deliberately omitted.** Pace will vary. Add `(date)` next to a milestone heading when it ships, and link to the version it shipped at: `✅ ({{date_today}}, shipped at v0.X.0)`.

> **Polish milestones (e.g. M2.5) may be inserted between feature milestones** when real usage surfaces rough edges. They are first-class, not deviations.

